{"tid":2496174,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國揸車行青山公路既人好撚低賤","createTime":"2021-04-19T15:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T15:42:43.000Z","uid":21149,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e658d93e938e476dfd3ac88ddf3e36a354539dbc","tid":2496174,"uid":21149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"青山公路根本就係路權撚既天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一家大細 0 gear踩馬路又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一班gear撚 20鳩幾架一齊踩到環法咁又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾個fd囝幾架平排hea踩chill下又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極致輕量化既gear撚一條友唔裝燈踩又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過點都好啦<br />\n紅燈都係得掛左牌既車一定要停姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲路權撚咁環保 又緊係唔係洗交牌費啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲腳賤私家車有咩事撞到班路權撚 仲可以食鳩人地車保獅子開大口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後情況容許下 一見到啲路權撚都要落車比個三鞠躬以示尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86f691ae5a3faba724028f6502e24a85c309da8","tid":2496174,"uid":21149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"上斜唔夠力，緊係S形咁行啦，落斜衝住落分分鐘可以推鳩私家車，呀屌又上斜啦慢慢扭先"}]}